org.jets3t.service
Class Jets3tProperties

java.lang.Object
  org.jets3t.service.Jets3tProperties

public class Jets3tProperties
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class to locate jets3t-specific properties files and make them available from a central place.

Properties are loaded from sources in the following order.

  1. jets3t.properties file in the classpath
  2. jets3t.properties file in the default jets3t home directory: Constants.DEFAULT_PREFERENCES_DIRECTORY
  3. System Properties
Properties sourced from later locations over-ride those sourced from prior locations. For example, if a property exists in jets3t.properties in the classpath and is also set as a system property, the system property version will be used.
